      "message": "Patch Set 3:\n\nTests received by maloo, run on CentOS release 6.5/x86_64: (https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/87302042-bf1e-11e3-84ad-52540035b04c).  Ran 23 tests.  4 tests failed: sanity-lfsck, sanity-quota, recovery-small, conf-sanity.",
