        "subject": "LU-4647 nodemap: support for getxattr",
        "message": "LU-4647 nodemap: support for getxattr\n\nAdd support to getxattr for nodemap id mapping. ACLs that map to the\nsquashed uid or gid are editted out of the acl before returned to the\nclient.\n\nSigned-off-by: Joshua Walgenbach <jjw@iu.edu>\nChange-Id: Icf19c85853ad5a6970dbb9e70755ff4d86a1a540\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
